cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with generating realistic images of humans based on a coarse sketch of the pose. 
2. cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper deals with generating images of humans with control over the specific instance or type of outfit worn by the user. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper proposes an end-to-end trainable network under the generative adversarial framework. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also possible as the paper deals with generating images of humans. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper proposes a novel approach for generating images of humans with control over the final appearance.
